'''新加坡體育城'''（{{lang-ms|Hab Sukan Singapura}}）是一座位於[[新加坡|新加坡]][[加冷|加冷]]全新落成的{{link-en|體育園區|Sports complex}}。它的位置為舊[[新加坡國家體育場|新加坡國家體育場]]的原址，2010年9月29日開始拆遷。<ref>{{cite news |first = Patwant |last = Singh |title = Consortium reveals horse shoe-shaped iconic design for Sports Hub |url = http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/267210/1/.html |publisher = [[Channel_NewsAsia|Channel NewsAsia]] |date = 29 March 2007 |accessdate = 2013-12-06 |archive-date = 2012-10-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121012125553/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/267210/1/.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>新加坡體育城的興建工程於2011年開始，2011年2月奠基，原计划2014年4月啟用，但后来因天气等其他因素延后至2014年6月。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.straitstimes.com/breaking-news/sports/story/singapore-sports-hub-project-due-completion-march-2014-20130610 | title=Singapore Sports Hub due for opening in April 2014 | publisher=[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]] | date=10 June 2013 | accessdate=10 July 2013 | archive-date=2013-12-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211161944/http://www.straitstimes.com/breaking-news/sports/story/singapore-sports-hub-project-due-completion-march-2014-20130610 | dead-url=no }}</ref>体育城最后于2015年6月26日正式竣工启用，由新加坡时任总理[[李显龙|李显龙]]主持开幕。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/education/pm-marks-youth-day-opens-sports-hub-in-front-of-50000-crowd|title=PM marks Youth Day, opens Sports Hub in front of 50,000 crowd|last=hermesauto|date=2015-07-26|work=[[海峡时报|海峡时报]] The Straits Times|access-date=2018-06-11|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629142803/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/education/pm-marks-youth-day-opens-sports-hub-in-front-of-50000-crowd|dead-url=no}}</ref>

